data.description: Have you been waiting for the perfect home on a cul-de-sac in Tatum Ranch? This is it! Sitting on an oversized lot, this two-story home boasts a grand entry, updated kitchen, formal dining room, family room, living room and HUGE bonus loft! Downstairs features wood & tile floors, while upstairs has new carpet & luxury vinyl plank. Spacious primary suite has vaulted ceilings, separate shower & garden tub, dual sinks and walk-in closet. With no neighbors directly behind, you will fall in love with the private backyard with so much room to make it your own!  Don't miss this! New Trane A/C Unit (2022)!
